page.text: Intersection: NC Highway 172 at SR 1516 (North Sneads Ferry Road)
Mekuria Engineering, Inc. ● Post Office Box 10505, Raleigh, NC 27605 ● www.mekuriaengineering.com ● phone: 919.833.8743
Data Collection Method: Jamar Count Board
1) Dixon Elementary School is located approximately 3 miles from
the studied intersection and was in session on the date of the
count, as were all Onslow County Schools.
2) Pedestrians were observed and counted – none were disabled.
4) Area lighting was not present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal
6) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of
7) Counter took breaks from 10:15 – 10:30 AM and 2:45 – 3:15 PM.
Data for these periods was interpolated.
8) Counter Notes: There was no posted speed limit on North Sneads Ferry Road. Several locals said traffic in
the NB direction on NC 172 backs up early in the morning (approximately 6:30 - 7:00 AM), in front of the gas
station, just south of this intersection. However the counter did not observe such backups during the count.
